# Pre-push gate. Runs the same `verify` chain CI runs so a coverage drop /
# attw regression / size budget bust fails the push before it ever hits
# GitHub Actions. Slower than pre-commit (~10s for verify on a clean cache),
# but only runs on push, which is rare relative to commits.
#
# Skip in an emergency with `git push --no-verify`. Don't make it a habit;
# the next CI run will surface what you skipped.

npm run verify
